The simplest term one can add to the Standard Model to obtain Eq.~\eqref{mixingHam} is the Pontecorvo-Maki-Nakagawa-Sakata (PMNS) matrix \cite{pontecorvoJETP68,makiPTP62}. Incorporating a Majorana mass term  that couples left-handed particles together is an addition to the Standard Model, $\mathcal{L}_\sm{}$, that appears as \cite{drewesIJMPE13}

